{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_10_03",
  "title": "神崎莉央 3話 また口紅を塗っちゃうわよ？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影スタジオ　自室風セット",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Filming Studio Room-style Set",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ようやくこの日がきたわね\nふふっ、腕……いえ、指が鳴るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Finally‚ this day has come.\nFufu‚ my arms… no‚ my fingers are itching to go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.0333333452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 9.9843312542
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "撮影のために、ここまでセットを組んでくれるなんてね\n衣装も部屋着みたいだし、リラックスして臨めそうだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They set up such an elaborate set just for filming.\nThe costume is like loungewear too‚ so I can approach this relaxed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6333333452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、随分余裕そうですけど\nマニキュアは塗れるようになったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ you seem quite confident‚ but\nhave you learned to apply nail polish?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8666666786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 24.6445579807
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "当然でしょ。貴方のメイクは私に任せてちょうだい\nこないだのでしっかりマスターしたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. Leave your makeup to me.\nI really mastered it the other day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2333333452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 31.868593943
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺じゃなくて、莉央さんのメイクなんですけど\nやっぱり撮影を延期してもらった方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not my makeup‚ it's Rio-san's makeup.\nMaybe we should have the filming postponed after all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2000000119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、冗談よ\n貴方、そうやってすぐ本気にするんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ okay‚ I was joking.\nYou always take things so seriously like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.4666666786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 44.412131671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "もう完璧よ。目をつぶってても塗れるくらい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm perfect now. I could apply it with my eyes closed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.412131671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 47.9014524737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "あの後、貴方の見てないところでも沢山練習したのよ？\nどんなことでも、努力すれば乗り越えられるものね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ I practiced a lot when you weren't watching‚ you know?\nWith effort‚ you can overcome anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8333343625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それは良かったです。俺をメイクして\n遊ばなければ、もっと良かったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's good. If you hadn't played around\nby putting makeup on me‚ it would have been even better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6000010292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 62.9737202602
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "あれで私もリラックス出来たのよ。ありがとう\n……私のおもちゃになってくれて、ふふ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That helped me relax too. Thank you\n…for becoming my toy‚ fufu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1333343625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 70.4110671638
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いまいち納得出来ませんが……まぁいいです\nそれより、撮影頑張って下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not entirely convinced‚ but… well‚ whatever.\nMore importantly‚ please do your best in the filming.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.9000010292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_rioroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "rioroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 77.9615660308
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、安心して見ていてちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ you can watch without concern.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9615660308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "角度はこれくらいでいいですか？\nもう少し右？　はい、分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this angle good?\nA little more to the right? Yes‚ understood.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.8000010292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "よそ見しながらでも、塗れてるのが凄い……？\nええ、もう慣れちゃってますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You think it's amazing I can paint even while looking away…?\nYes‚ I'm used to it now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4604785666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、仕事柄何度も塗ってますから……\nなんなら足の指でも出来ますよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I've applied it many times due to work…\nI could even do my toenails if you want?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.3000050981,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（凄い。余裕だ……ついこの間まで）\n（片手で一時間かかっていた人とは思えない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Amazing. She looks so composed… I can't believe）\n（this is the same person who took an hour for one hand recently.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.6666692216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（まあ莉央さんが今まで乗り越えてきたことを）\n（思えば、これくらいの壁は越えて当然か）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Well‚ considering all the things Rio-san has overcome up until now‚）\n（a hurdle like this is only natural for her to surpass.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.5375661439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "画になる手の角度は、こんな感じじゃないですか？\nはい、目線はカメラのままでも大丈夫です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The photogenic hand angle is something like this‚ right?\nYes‚ keeping my gaze on the camera is fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.3000061153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "もっといろいろ試してみますか？\n……え、もうOK？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shall we try a few more things?\n…Eh‚ we're done already?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7333379227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "可能なら、別バージョンも？　ええ喜んで\nいいわよね、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If possible‚ another version too? Sure‚ I'd be glad to.\nThat's fine‚ right‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.6000015376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "はい。今日は一日、CMのために確保してますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. We've reserved the whole day for the CM.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.8921921209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの撮影についての貴方の意見も聞きたいわね\n一度、打ち合わせをしましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd like to hear your opinion about the earlier filming too.\nShall we have a meeting once?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.5666641352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影からしばらくして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some Time After Filming",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.5497630711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.8630990144
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.8630990144
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "……渋滞でタクシーが遅れてる？　またなの？\nいいわ。次の現場は近いから、歩いて行きましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…The taxi is delayed due to traffic? Again?\nWell‚ the next location is close. So let's walk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.4333226638,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、最近、莉央さんを走らせたり\n歩かせたりばっかりで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ lately I've been making Rio-san run\nand walk all the time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.2666559972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.3672521866
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "貴方のせいじゃないんだし、仕方ないわ\nそれより、早く行きましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not your fault‚ so it can't be helped.\nMore importantly‚ let's go quickly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.599991365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、莉央さん、見て下さい\nあの街頭モニターで流れてるCM――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Rio-san‚ look at that.\nThe CM playing on that street monitor――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.199991365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.6584083832
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "今日は、ピンク、それとも赤？\nその日の気分で、いつでも変われるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ pink or red?\nYou can switch it up anytime‚ depending on your mood.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.999991365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "可愛いも綺麗も指先から――\nシャオール",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From your fingertips‚ both cute and beautiful――\nShaorl",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.6666580317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.9565487818
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "CM、今日から流れてたのね\nふふ、こうして外の大きなモニターで見るのは新鮮ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The CM started airing today.\nFufu‚ seeing it on a giant screen outside is so new to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.5666580317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんの立ち居振る舞いが綺麗だって\n凄く評判いいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san's graceful behavior\nhas a really good reputation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.199991365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 206.1983859815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、だからまた\n新しいCMの仕事がきたんでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ that's why\nwe got another CM job‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.1333246984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 211.7736240981
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、今度はアクセサリーです\n忙しいのに、また仕事を増やしてしまいましたが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ this time it's accessories.\nYou're busy‚ but I've added more work again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.0666580317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 222.4214725812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "私がいいって言ってるんだから、いいの\nほら、急ぐわよ！　次の現場が待ってるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I say it's fine‚ then it's fine.\nCome on‚ let's hurry! The next location is waiting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.4214725812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "どんな理由であれ、仕事に遅刻なんて\n絶対ダメなんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For any reason‚ being late for work\nis absolutely unacceptable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 228.899991365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 230.6954431491
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（BIG4になっても、莉央さんは変わらない）\n（仕事に対して真摯で、誇りを持っている）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Even after becoming BIG4‚ Rio-san hasn't changed）\n（She's sincere about work and takes pride in it）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.7333246984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（彼女がリーダーでいる限り）\n（LizNoirは大丈夫だ。きっともっと成長出来る）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（As long as she remains the leader‚）\n（LizNoir will be fine. They can surely grow even more）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.5555887984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 245.5049214003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほら、いつまでも立ち止まってないで\nさっさと歩く！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ don't just stand there forever.\nWalk faster!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.3147540283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio025.m4a",
      "text": "あんまりぼーっとしてると\nまた口紅を塗っちゃうわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you space out too much‚\nI'll put lipstick on you again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.3333308019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 254.7981246429
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "俺で遊ぶのは勘弁して下さい。あっ、橋本さんとか\n他の人のことも、あんまりいじらないで下さいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't toy with me. Oh‚ Hashimoto-san and\nothers too‚ please don't tease them too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.3999974685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 263.1731358963
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_10_03-rio026.m4a",
      "text": "あんなこと、他の人にする訳ないでしょ\n貴方にしか、しないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wouldn't do something like that to other people.\nI only do it to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 267.2666641352,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}